  RESULTADOS VALIDADOS
================================================================================

  ISOP 27/02:  OTD=100%  OTD-D=100%  tardy=0  earliness=5.6d  setups=125
  ISOP 17/03:  OTD=100%  OTD-D=100%  tardy=0  earliness=5.4d  setups=134
  396 testes passam. Pipeline deterministico. <500ms modo quick.
  17/17 constraints PASS em ambos ISOPs.


================================================================================
  CONSTANTES GLOBAIS
